JIRA SEARCH - Confluence settings

Click big + to the very right
Select "Other Macros"

	- Expand - Creates arrow to expand
	- Status - Shows Status as in "in progress" "closed" "open" "on hold" like on project page
	- Advanced Tables - Table plus
	- "Insert Jira Issue/Filter" to show report of Bugs/Issues/Test Cases made and More








	- To have "Expand" macros on Confluence Personal Page
		1 Step. Create Project Template
		2 Step. Content Report Table
		

